# DEVELOPMENT ROADMAP FOR scMultiome-GRN

> **Role:** Senior Bioinformatician & Nextflow Developer
> **Objective:** Refactor the legacy scripts (R, Python, Bash) into a clean
> Nextflow DSL2 pipeline optimized for a 1-hour live-demo masterclass.
> **Stack:** R (Seurat/Signac/Cicero) + Python (Scanpy/CellOracle) +
> Nextflow DSL2 + Docker + GitHub Actions.
> **Scope (validated):** AMBICIOUS — full CellOracle pipeline + in silico
> perturbation with vector fields, plus CI/CD with GHCR publication.

