## Phase 5 — Workflow Orchestration (`main.nf` + `workflows/multiome_grn.nf`)
- [x] Implement `workflows/multiome_grn.nf`:
  - [x] `workflow GRN_PIPELINE` with `take:` and `emit:` blocks (DSL2 idiom).
  - [x] Calls `PREPROCESS_ATAC(ch_input)`.
  - [x] Calls `INFER_GRN(PREPROCESS_ATAC.out.preproc..., params...)`.
  - [x] Emits `ch_plots` and `ch_grn_artifacts`.
  - [x] Sub-workflow includes PREPROCESS_ATAC and INFER_GRN modules directly.
- [x] Implement `main.nf`:
  - [x] `nextflow.enable.dsl = 2`.
  - [x] Includes GRN_PIPELINE sub-workflow.
  - [x] Channel wiring from `params.input` via `Channel.fromPath`.
  - [x] Logs key params at the top of the workflow.
- [x] **Validation 1:** `nextflow run main.nf --help` lists every param — **confirmed**.
- [x] **Validation 2:** `nextflow run main.nf -preview` shows both processes in the DAG — **confirmed**.
- [x] **Validation 3:** end-to-end execution with `-profile test` produces all 4 PREPROCESS outputs + 9 INFER outputs — **confirmed**.

