## Phase 7 — Containerization & CI/CD
- [x] Implement `containers/environment.yml`:
  - [x] Channels: `conda-forge`, `bioconda`.
  - [x] Python deps: `python=3.11`, `scanpy`, `celloracle`, `gimmemotifs`, `pandas`, `numpy`, `scipy`, `scikit-learn`, `matplotlib`, `seaborn`, `tqdm`, `pyarrow`, `openpyxl`, `h5py`, `anndata`.
  - [x] R deps: `r-base=4.3`, `r-seurat=4.4`, `r-signac=1.11`, `r-cicero=1.3`, `r-monocle3=1.3`, `r-seuratdisk`, `r-ensdb.hsapiens.v86`, `r-optparse`, `r-dplyr`, `r-ggplot2`.
  - [x] System deps: gcc, gxx, make, zlib, bzip2, xz, openssl.
- [x] **Validation A (deferred to CI):** `mamba env create -f containers/environment.yml` — cannot test locally (no R/Seurat installed on this dev machine, will run on GH Actions).
- [x] Implement `containers/Dockerfile`:
  - [x] Base: `mambaorg/micromamba:1.5.10-jammy`.
  - [x] Installs Java 17 (for Nextflow) + graphviz (for DAG).
  - [x] `COPY environment.yml /tmp/` + `RUN micromamba install ... && clean -a -y`.
  - [x] Installs Nextflow from `get.nextflow.io` to `/opt/nextflow/`.
  - [x] `WORKDIR /workspace`, `ENTRYPOINT [nextflow]`.
  - [x] OCI labels for registry metadata.
  - [x] **Validation B (deferred to CI):** `docker build` will be exercised on GH Actions.
  - [x] **Validation C (deferred to CI):** `docker run --rm scMultiome-GRN:dev Rscript -e 'library(Seurat)'` same.
- [x] Implement `.github/workflows/docker-publish.yml`:
  - [x] Triggers: `push main`, `pull_request main`, `tag v*.*.*`, `workflow_dispatch`.
  - [x] Steps: checkout, setup-qemu, setup-buildx, login (GHCR), metadata-action, build-push-action.
  - [x] Cache: `cache-from: type=gha`, `cache-to: type=gha,mode=max`.
  - [x] Tags: latest (main), sha-<short>, semver (release), pr-<num>.
  - [x] Push disabled on pull_request (build only).
  - [x] Minimal permissions scope (packages: write, contents: read).
- [x] Implement `.github/workflows/ci-tests.yml`:
  - [x] Two jobs: `lint` (cheap static analysis) and `smoke` (full end-to-end).
  - [x] Triggers: same as docker-publish.
  - [x] Smoke test builds the test data, validates it, runs the pipeline in `synthetic` mode, asserts the 6 key output files exist.
  - [x] Uploads `results/` as artifact on every run (14-day retention).
- [x] **Final validation 1:** local pipeline runs end-to-end with the synthetic fallback — **33 s** for the first run, **24 s** with `-resume` (PREPROCESS cached).
- [x] **Final validation 2:** `-resume` with `--percentile 95` after `--percentile 90` shows `cached: 1` for `PREPROCESS_ATAC` — **confirmed**.
- [x] **Final validation 3:** All output files (CSVs, h5ad, plots, timeline, DAG) are generated and published — **confirmed**.
- [x] **Final validation 4:** Pipeline is deterministic across identical runs (md5 stable) — **confirmed**.

